OL,3,CCompany fined more than #100,000 after
OL,4,Cman falls 10 metres through barn roof
OL,6,FA company has been fined more than
OL,7,F#100,000 after a man was seriously
OL,8,Finjured when he fell through a barn
OL,9,Froof in Southampton.
OL,11,FThe 37-year-old from Bursledon had
OL,12,Fbeen helping his friend repair a fire-
OL,13,Fdamaged storage barn at Dodwell Farm
OL,14,FLimited on Pylands Lane in February
OL,15,Flast year, when he fell around 10
OL,16,Fmetres below.
