OL,3,CCompany fined more than #100,000 after
OL,4,Cman falls 10 metres through barn roof
OL,6,FHe had been at the top of a sloped
OL,7,Froof fixing new panels to timbers, but
OL,8,Fthe Health and Safety Executive (HSE)
OL,9,Fsay they were not strong enough to
OL,10,Fhold his weight. The roof gave way
OL,11,Fwhen he stood on them and he fell
OL,12,Fthrough.
OL,14,FThe injuries he suffered were severe
OL,15,Fand he spent an extended period in
OL,16,Fhospital.
OL,18,FAn investigation by HSE found that
OL,19,Fsafety measures such as barriers,
OL,20,Fnetting or access equipment were not
OL,21,Fin place.
