OL,3,CCompany fined more than #100,000 after
OL,4,Cman falls 10 metres through barn roof
OL,6,FThe findings found Dodwell Farm
OL,7,FLimited had failed to take appropriate
OL,8,Fprecautions to ensure the safety of
OL,9,Fworkers, and others affected by the
OL,10,Fwork, when replacing the barn roof.
OL,12,FThe company pleaded guilty to
OL,13,Fbreaching a Health and Safety Act and
OL,14,Fwas fined #133,000 on Friday 3 January
OL,15,F2025.
OL,17,FAfter the hearing, HSE inspector
OL,18,FNicola Pinckney said: "Too many
OL,19,Fworkers are injured and killed every
OL,20,Fyear as a result of falling from
OL,21,Fheight.
OL,1,W~s1x0~s1~s hw1~k4~c1 hw}h7}j7}   G3/4
