OL,3,CCompany fined more than #100,000 after
OL,4,Cman falls 10 metres through barn roof
OL,6,F"The sentence imposed on Dodwell Farm
OL,7,FLimited should underline to everyone
OL,8,Fwho carries out work at height that
OL,9,Fthe courts, and HSE, take a failure to
OL,10,Ffollow the regulations extremely
OL,11,Fseriously.
OL,13,F"Measures to prevent the accident,
OL,14,Fsuch as avoiding working from the
OL,15,Froof, protecting fragile surfaces and
OL,16,Fhaving netting in place, are well
OL,17,Fknown and readily available.
OL,19,F"HSE will not hesitate to take action
OL,20,Fagainst companies which do not do all
OL,21,Fthat they should to keep people safe."
